Interface IAlertDeliveryMechanism

public interface IAlertDeliveryMechanism

Information about a mechanism for delivering an alert.

Method Summary

          Gets a String containing additional data for this IAlertDeliveryMechanism.

Method Detail

getTypeId

String getTypeId()
Gets a String containing the type of this IAlertDeliveryMechanism. This is the identifier of one of the PropertyTypes in the property group named "Alert Delivery Methods" of the LinkType named "Alert Feed Subscription" in the current Schema.

Returns:
See above.

getData

String getData()
Gets a String containing additional data for this IAlertDeliveryMechanism. For example, if email messages were the mechanism by which alerts were delivered, then the data could be an email address. This can value can be empty if no additional data is required.

Returns:
See above.
